{"id":2135,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/2135","type":2,"name":"鴉 -KARAS-","name_cn":"鸦 -KARAS-","summary":"　　《鸦 -KARAS-》，由日本动画泰山北斗吉田龙夫所创立的龙之子Production制作，是为了成立四十周年纪念所推出的OVA作品。总共有六话，2005年11月开始发售第一话。在2005年发行了三话，而第四话到第六话在2007年中以后才发行。\r\n　　《鸦 -KARAS-》是一部结合格斗、侦探和鬼怪，融合奇幻与科幻的动画，配乐上由布拉格交响乐团演出，并获得2006第五回东京国际动画（东京国际アニメアワード）OVA部门优秀作品奖。\r\n　　《鸦 KARAS》的故事描述了一个充满妖怪的虚构新宿里，一个名叫乙羽的人与新宿的事。乙羽是一名“鸦”，就是由城市（由百合音作为城市意志的代理人）所认可而成的一个强大守护者。在故事里，前任的“鸦”——回向，意图控制他以前保护的新宿。而乙羽和其他妖怪以及其他的“鸦”则试着对抗他。","eps":[{"id":12194,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/12194","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"鴉開眼","name_cn":"鸦开眼","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":10,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":12195,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/12195","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"火炎輪","name_cn":"火炎轮","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":12196,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/12196","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"滅覺醒","name_cn":"灭觉醒","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":3,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":12197,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/12197","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"人乙羽","name_cn":"人乙羽","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":5,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":12198,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/12198","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"幻想区","name_cn":"幻想区","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":3,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":12199,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/12199","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"真伝説","name_cn":"真传说","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":6,"desc":"","status":"Air"}],"eps_count":6,"air_date":"2005-05-28","air_weekday":6,"rating":{"total":1163,"count":{"1":2,"2":0,"3":6,"4":16,"5":32,"6":167,"7":362,"8":416,"9":129,"10":33},"score":7.4},"rank":1087,"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/9a/49/2135_jLBz1.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/9a/49/2135_jLBz1.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/9a/49/2135_jLBz1.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/9a/49/2135_jLBz1.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/9a/49/2135_jLBz1.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":647,"collect":1587,"doing":62,"on_hold":140,"dropped":50},"crt